choices.text:
I do not have Enough time Blessed Enough Time to sleep.

Mostly I sleep on the buses , flea-market alleys, a borrowed sofa when my housekeeper is sleeping…..so I decided to design my sofa which allows me to sleep comfortably , and read on the long bus or train ride .

It allows me to work on my laptop , take notes ,study using my small laptop next to my reclined and still sleeping self…..and wake up home.

When folded and propped against the wall, it allows me to keep on working on my laptop, or continue reading my book without disturbing anyone.

You can tell about your reason to create: Creativity for me , is my passion, it’s the air I breath.

It is the reason why I don’t usually make many friends.

I am exclusively focusing at my purse and accessories label , Akioudesigns. com. Nothing is more important to me than my sketchbook, my design techniques ,and my fabric collection .

If I am bored, designing gives me solace, it makes me happy, and it keeps waiting for me in the dark, until I focus on anything else.

So in a sense it’s my lover

Please describe a typical workday : I can get up as early as 5AM ( after having fallen asleep on my bureau at 2 to do researches on the web ) and continue my drawings until 9, and then head to L’ecole des Beaux-Arts de Dakar,
